snippet.description:

I hope everyone had a fun time celebrating the countdown, or even just watching the countdown at home. Either way, why not have a nice start of the year by watching our 'La Vie En Rose' cover ğŸ¤­ Doing the MAMA version to celebrate the first cover of 2025, on this channel, just made so much sense to me and I'm glad that I finally got to cover IZ*ONE's iconic debut (I miss them ğŸ˜) I decided to add my own choreography to the beginning of the song because in the actual performance they don't really do anything. Hope you guys like it! Everyone in this project did AMAZING and I'm so happy with how it turned out â˜ºï¸

This channel has grown SO much for the past year and I never would've imagined I'd be where I am right now. So I just want to thank all of you guys for your support, you guys are the real heroes â¤ï¸

As always thank you to my friends for being in this cover, thank you to Chan for filming and thank you to everyone who came to help out on the day ğŸ’“

I hope you guys enjoyed the video and consider subscribing if you want to see more of my content ğŸ˜ Here's to 2025 being an amazing year for all of us ğŸ¥³

"We made it, we hit the 100K milestone! We would have never imagined hitting that milestone since we started our journey as UNLXMITED. This is a crazy accomplishment, and we just wanted to say thank you to everyone who joined us on this journey or will join us once our journey continues in the future! Funny enough, not only are we celebrating something special, but did you know this year marks the 10th anniversary of 'Growl' being released? We are still speechless from this huge achievement, and we just want to say thank you from the bottom of our hearts! We wouldn't be here without you guys!
